title: Harvey on time, Collins a cutup and mollified Mets off to LA

> Sports Harvey on time, Collins a cutup and mollified Mets off to LA New York Mets manager Terry Collins, right, talks with pitcher Matt Harvey during a workout at Citi Field, Wednesday, Oct. 7, 2015 in New York. The Mets will play the Los Angeles Dodgers in a National League Division Series starting Friday in Los Angeles.. (AP Photo/Seth Wenig)
